<h2>New Assignment: {{assignmentTitle}}</h2>

<p>Hi {{studentName}},</p>

<p>Your teacher <strong>{{teacherName}}</strong> has assigned you a new vocabulary exercise in the class <strong>{{className}}</strong>.</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 18px;">Assignment Details:</h3>
    <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li><strong>Title:</strong> {{assignmentTitle}}</li>
        <li><strong>Words to learn:</strong> {{wordCount}} words</li>
        <li><strong>Exercise type:</strong> {{exerciseType}}</li>
        <li><strong>Due date:</strong> {{formatDate dueDate}}</li>
    </ul>
</div>

{{> button url=assignmentUrl text="Start Assignment"}}

<div style="background-color: #e8f5e8; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #352D24;">
    <p style="margin: 0; color: #2e7d32;">
        Good luck with your learning! Remember, consistency is key to mastering vocabulary.
    </p>
</div>
